THE BILLS (acronym)

TIME - Configure the time to be correct in user EXEC mode
HOSTNAME - then give it a host name (conf t, hostname)
ENABLE - Put an enable password on it
BANNER - for legal reasons, put a banner of the router.
IP DOMAIN-LOOKUP - turn this off, bad, slow and insecure.
LINE CONSOLE - put a password on the console. don't forget the login command
LINE VTY - use 0 and 15, which will cover all the possible vty lines. 
SERVICE PASSWORD-ENCRYPTION - secure the running config so it doesnt show things in plain text.
